License:    GPL+ or Artistic
URL:        https://metacpan.org/release/Pod-Plainer
Source0:    https://cpan.metacpan.org/authors/id/R/RM/RMBARKER/Pod-Plainer-%{version}.tar.gz#/perl-Pod-Plainer-%{version}.tar.gz
